{"word":"καταζεύγνυμι","slug":"καταζεύγνυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταζεύγνυμι</b></el> <el>(and <el>-ύω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ζεύξω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to yoke together, yoke</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be united</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, also, <i>to be straitened, confined, imprisoned</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}